column2:
For example, if using terminal:

curl --request POST \
  --url https://preview.api.climatiq.io/autopilot/v1-preview3/suggest \
  --header "Authorization: Bearer $CLIMATIQ_API_KEY" \
  --data '{
    "suggest": {
        "domain": "general",
        "text": "Cement"
    },
    "max_suggestions": 2
}'
